Claire's

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the retailer. For other uses, see Claire (disambiguation).

Claire's Stores, Inc.





Formerly called

Fashion Tress Industries (1961–1973)


Industry
Retail


Founded
1961


Headquarters
Hoffman Estates, Illinois, U.S.



